WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.500 --> 00:00:03.133
Miss, you almost hit me

2
00:00:03.133 --> 00:00:04.400
You have to apologize to me.

3
00:00:05.966 --> 00:00:08.166
Why isn't this car moving?

4
00:00:08.866 --> 00:00:10.400
Dad?

5
00:00:13.466 --> 00:00:14.833
Dad?

6
00:00:18.966 --> 00:00:19.766
Dad?

7
00:00:21.133 --> 00:00:22.466
Don't scare me

8
00:00:23.300 --> 00:00:25.433
What's wrong with you?

9
00:00:25.533 --> 00:00:26.533
Why are you still standing?

10
00:00:26.533 --> 00:00:27.766
Come and help

11
00:00:30.333 --> 00:00:31.400
My car has broken down!

12
00:00:31.400 --> 00:00:33.666
Can you help me get my dad to the hospital?

13
00:00:33.700 --> 00:00:34.700
Too late to go to the hospital

14
00:00:35.366 --> 00:00:36.800
The hospital is just ahead.

15
00:00:36.966 --> 00:00:39.166
Just help me get my dad to the hospital

16
00:00:40.200 --> 00:00:41.000
Ah!

17
00:00:41.766 --> 00:00:43.133
Here's 10,000 dollars

18
00:00:43.133 --> 00:00:45.366
I'll give you 100,000 at the hospital

19
00:00:46.366 --> 00:00:48.066
Ah, not enough, right?

20
00:00:48.066 --> 00:00:49.000
I have 1 million

21
00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:49.866
I'll transfer it to you.

22
00:00:49.866 --> 00:00:52.900
Hurry up, what are you doing?

23
00:00:55.333 --> 00:00:56.700
What did you do?

24
00:00:56.866 --> 00:00:59.400
Dad, stop crying

25
00:00:59.500 --> 00:01:00.833
He was poisoned

26
00:01:01.000 --> 00:01:02.566
I got his heart

27
00:01:02.766 --> 00:01:04.233
He can still slow down for half an hour

28
00:01:04.366 --> 00:01:05.466
You are not allowed to go

29
00:01:05.666 --> 00:01:07.200
If something happened to my dad

30
00:01:07.200 --> 00:01:08.500
I want you to pay

31
00:01:09.100 --> 00:01:10.800
He'll wake up in three minutes

32
00:01:11.133 --> 00:01:12.666
Then you take him to the hospital

33
00:01:13.066 --> 00:01:14.100
I'll go first

34
00:01:14.100 --> 00:01:15.133
If something goes wrong

35
00:01:15.133 --> 00:01:16.633
You can find me at No. 30 Liuxia

36
00:01:17.300 --> 00:01:18.100
Hello

37
00:01:18.666 --> 00:01:21.200
Dad, wait for me

